<% content_for :landing_page, true %>
<% content_for :title do %><%= installation_brand_name %> — One inbox for every customer channel<% end %>
<% content_for :meta_description do %>
  <%= installation_brand_name %> by SamaBrains Solutions unifies WhatsApp, email, website chat, and social messaging in one workspace — with <%= installation_captain_name %>, automations, and local Pesapal billing in UGX.
<% end %>
<% captain = installation_captain_name %>
<section class="landing-hero">
  <div class="landing-hero-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <p class="landing-eyebrow">Customer support platform · Built for African businesses</p>
  <h1 class="landing-hero-title">Every customer message.<br>One calm workspace.</h1>
  <p class="landing-hero-lead">
    <strong><%= installation_brand_name %></strong> brings WhatsApp, email, live chat, and social DMs together so your team can reply faster,
    collaborate clearly, and never lose context — with AI that learns from your own help content.
  </p>
  <div class="landing-hero-actions">
    <a href="/app/auth/signup" class="landing-btn landing-btn-primary">Start free — Starter plan</a>
    <a href="<%= pricing_path %>" class="landing-btn landing-btn-secondary">View pricing</a>
  </div>
  <p class="landing-hero-note">No credit card for Starter · Pay with Pesapal on upgrade · Operated by SamaBrains Solutions</p>
</section>

<section class="landing-channels" aria-label="Supported channels">
  <p class="landing-section-label">Connect where your customers already are</p>
  <div class="landing-channel-row">
    <span class="landing-channel-pill">WhatsApp</span>
    <span class="landing-channel-pill">Gmail &amp; email</span>
    <span class="landing-channel-pill">Website chat</span>
    <span class="landing-channel-pill">Messenger &amp; Instagram</span>
    <span class="landing-channel-pill">SMS &amp; API</span>
    <span class="landing-channel-pill">Help Center</span>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="landing-section">
  <div class="landing-section-head">
    <h2>The problem we solve</h2>
    <p>Customers message you everywhere. Your team shouldn’t chase threads across five different apps.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="landing-card-grid landing-card-grid-3">
    <article class="landing-card">
      <span class="landing-card-icon landing-card-icon-blue" aria-hidden="true">◎</span>
      <h3>Scattered conversations</h3>
      <p>Email in Gmail, orders on WhatsApp, questions on Instagram — no shared history or ownership.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="landing-card">
      <span class="landing-card-icon landing-card-icon-violet" aria-hidden="true">↻</span>
      <h3>Slow, inconsistent replies</h3>
      <p>Messages get missed, handoffs are messy, and customers repeat themselves on every channel.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="landing-card">
      <span class="landing-card-icon landing-card-icon-emerald" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
      <h3>One workspace for your team</h3>
      <p><%= installation_brand_name %> unifies channels, assigns owners, tracks SLAs, and keeps every reply in context.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="landing-section landing-section-alt">
  <div class="landing-section-head">
    <h2>Everything included on every plan</h2>
    <p>Starter, Growth, and Business all ship the full product. You scale by <strong>agent seats</strong> and monthly <strong>Copilot</strong> usage — not locked features.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="landing-card-grid landing-card-grid-2">
    <article class="landing-feature">
      <h3>Unified inbox</h3>
      <p>Assign, label, note, and search conversations across every connected channel.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="landing-feature">
      <h3><%= installation_captain_name %></h3>
      <p>Auto-reply from your documents and FAQs; Copilot drafts for agents. <a href="<%= guide_page_path('captain') %>">Learn how <%= installation_captain_name %> works</a>.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="landing-feature">
      <h3>Campaigns</h3>
      <p>Proactive outreach on website chat, SMS, and WhatsApp templates.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="landing-feature">
      <h3>Automations &amp; SLA</h3>
      <p>Rules, macros, canned responses, and response-time policies.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="landing-feature">
      <h3>Help Center</h3>
      <p>Publish articles customers can search — and feed <%= installation_captain_name %> the same knowledge.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="landing-feature">
      <h3>Reports &amp; CRM</h3>
      <p>Contacts, companies, CSAT, agent performance, and integrations like LeadSquared.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="landing-section">
  <div class="landing-section-head">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p>Go live in an afternoon — start small, add channels as you grow.</p>
  </div>
  <ol class="landing-steps">
    <li>
      <span class="landing-step-num">1</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Create your workspace</strong>
        <p><a href="/app/auth/signup">Sign up free</a> on Starter. Invite agents from Settings → Agents.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="landing-step-num">2</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Connect your channels</strong>
        <p>Add WhatsApp, Gmail, website widget, or social inboxes. See the <a href="<%= guide_path %>">User Guide</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="landing-step-num">3</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Reply with confidence</strong>
        <p>Let <%= installation_captain_name %> handle first-line questions, then hand off to humans when it matters.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>

<section class="landing-section landing-ai-band">
  <div class="landing-ai-inner">
    <div>
      <p class="landing-section-label"><%= installation_captain_name %></p>
      <h2>AI that answers from <em>your</em> knowledge — not guesswork</h2>
      <p>Upload docs and URLs, approve FAQs, connect <%= installation_captain_name %> to WhatsApp or web chat, and hand off to your team when the issue needs a human.</p>
      <a href="<%= guide_page_path('captain') %>" class="landing-link-arrow"><%= installation_captain_name %> setup guide →</a>
    </div>
    <ul class="landing-ai-list">
      <li>Documents → auto-generated searchable FAQs</li>
      <li>Scenarios for billing, sales, and support flows</li>
      <li>Custom tools to call your APIs</li>
      <li>Copilot sidebar for agent draft replies</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<% if converra_plans.present? %>
<section class="landing-section" id="pricing">
  <div class="landing-section-head">
    <h2>Simple pricing in UGX</h2>
    <p>Start free. Upgrade when you need more agents or Copilot capacity. Pay with Pesapal — mobile money, M-Pesa, and cards.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="landing-pricing-grid">
    <% converra_plans.each do |slug, plan| %>
      <article class="landing-price-card<%= ' landing-price-card-featured' if slug == 'growth' %>">
        <% if slug == 'growth' %><span class="landing-price-badge">Popular</span><% end %>
        <h3><%= plan['name'] %></h3>
        <p class="landing-price-amount">
          <% if plan['price_ugx'].to_i.zero? %>
            Free
          <% else %>
            <%= number_with_delimiter(plan['price_ugx']) %> <span>UGX/mo</span>
          <% end %>
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><%= plan.dig('limits', 'agents') %> agent<%= plan.dig('limits', 'agents').to_i == 1 ? '' : 's' %></li>
          <li><%= number_with_delimiter(plan.dig('limits', 'captain_responses')) %> Copilot replies / month</li>
          <li>All channels &amp; features</li>
        </ul>
        <% if plan['price_ugx'].to_i.zero? %>
          <a href="/app/auth/signup" class="landing-btn landing-btn-primary landing-btn-block">Get started</a>
        <% else %>
          <a href="/app/login" class="landing-btn landing-btn-secondary landing-btn-block">Sign in to upgrade</a>
        <% end %>
      </article>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <p class="landing-pricing-foot"><a href="<%= pricing_path %>">Full pricing details →</a></p>
</section>
<% end %>

<section class="landing-section">
  <div class="landing-section-head">
    <h2>Built for teams like yours</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="landing-audience">
    <span>E-commerce &amp; retail</span>
    <span>SaaS &amp; tech startups</span>
    <span>Professional services</span>
    <span>Hospitality &amp; local business</span>
    <span>NGOs &amp; memberships</span>
    <span>Solo founders on Starter</span>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="landing-section landing-trust">
  <div class="landing-section-head">
    <h2>Trust &amp; privacy</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="landing-trust-grid">
    <article class="landing-card landing-card-compact">
      <h3>Google &amp; Gmail</h3>
      <p>When you connect Gmail, <%= installation_brand_name %> uses OAuth only to read and send support email for that inbox — not for ads or unrelated purposes. Revoke access anytime in <a href="https://myaccount.google.com/permissions" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Account permissions</a>.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="landing-card landing-card-compact">
      <h3>Policies</h3>
      <p>Read our <a href="<%= "#{legal_site_url}/privacy" %>">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="<%= "#{legal_site_url}/terms" %>">Terms of Service</a>. For businesses and authorized staff — not a consumer social network.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="landing-card landing-card-compact">
      <h3>Operator</h3>
      <p><strong>SamaBrains Solutions</strong><br>
      <a href="mailto:info@samabrains.com">info@samabrains.com</a><br>
      <a href="<%= legal_site_url %>"><%= legal_site_url.sub(%r{^https?://}, '') %></a></p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="landing-cta-band">
  <h2>Ready to stop juggling inboxes?</h2>
  <p>Join teams using <%= installation_brand_name %> to support customers on WhatsApp, email, and chat — from one place.</p>
  <div class="landing-hero-actions">
    <a href="/app/auth/signup" class="landing-btn landing-btn-primary">Create free workspace</a>
    <a href="<%= guide_path %>" class="landing-btn landing-btn-ghost">Read the User Guide</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="landing-footer">
  <nav aria-label="Footer">
    <a href="<%= guide_path %>">User Guide</a>
    <a href="<%= pricing_path %>">Pricing</a>
    <a href="<%= "#{legal_site_url}/privacy" %>">Privacy</a>
    <a href="<%= "#{legal_site_url}/terms" %>">Terms</a>
    <a href="mailto:info@samabrains.com">Contact</a>
  </nav>
  <p>© <%= Time.current.year %> SamaBrains Solutions · <%= installation_brand_name %></p>
</footer>
